theorem Topology.P1_iff_isOpen_of_isClosed {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA_closed : IsClosed (A : Set X)) :
    Topology.P1 A ↔ IsOpen (A : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hP1
    have hEq :=
      closure_interior_eq_of_isClosed_and_P1 (A := A) hA_closed hP1
    exact isOpen_of_closure_interior_eq (A := A) hEq
  · intro hOpen
    exact P1_of_isOpen (A := A) hOpen
